author: Gerry Moriarty
title: Coronavirus: ‘Emerging signs’ social distancing having effect in North
description: Fatalities in NI rise by three to 73 as chief medical officer warns against complacency
content:
There are some tentative signs that social distancing measures are having an effect in tackling Covid-19 in Northern Ireland, the Norths chief medical officer Dr Michael McBride has reported.
